system.description: When you plug into the cosmic aether and tune out of this world, roll + Freak.

failure.label: Complications...
failure.value: You realize something dangerous or terrible; the GM will tell you what, and shift your Labels accordingly.

partial.label: Partial success
partial.value: You come to a new, interesting insight about your current problems and situation; the GM will tell you what.

success.label: Success!
success.value: You come to a new, interesting insight about your current problems and situation; the GM will tell you what. You can also shift your own Labels according to match your new understanding.
